<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.15/dist/tailwind.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <title>Navigation Bar</title>
  </head>
  <style>
    @font-face {
      font-family: myFont;
      src: url(Chivo.ttf);
    }
    body {
      background-image: url("Images/backgournd.png");
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-attachment: fixed;
	  background-size:100%;
      background-position-y: 100%;
      font-family: myFont;
    }
    p {
      font-family: myFont;
    }
  </style>
  <body>
    <div class="container justify-center m-36">
      <p class="txt text-4xl ">
        Harvesting Prosperity Together: Bridging the Gap in Agriculture Trade.
      </p>
      <br />
      <p class="mx-48">
        You can locate the available stock and we can break the gap between the
        farmer and exporter
      </p>
    </div>
    <!--Code for the white screen-->
    <div class="whitebox m-80 w-full mx-0 mb-0">
      <hr class="w-full h-1 bg-black" />
      <div class="flex box w-screen bg-white h-full">
        <div class="img w-1/2"><img src="Images/v2.avif" alt="" /></div>
        <div class="txt w-1/2 pb-10 bg-white">
          <h1 class="underline text-center text-2xl mt-10 mb-10">Importance</h1>
          <p class="bg-white">
            Supporting local farmers by purchasing their crops at reliable
            prices and establishing direct communication between farmers and
            export companies, free from intermediaries, is of paramount
            importance. This approach fosters a multitude of benefits that
            extend far beyond the agricultural sector. Firstly, it ensures that
            farmers receive fair compensation for their hard work and
            dedication, bolstering their livelihoods and encouraging them to
            continue producing quality crops. Moreover, direct communication
            allows for a more transparent exchange of information and
            requirements, enabling farmers to tailor their production to market
            demands more effectively. By cutting out middlemen, both farmers and
            export companies can reduce costs, leading to more competitive
            prices for consumers. Additionally, this practice promotes
            sustainability by reducing the carbon footprint associated with
            transporting goods through multiple channels. Overall, supporting
            local farmers and facilitating direct communication between them and
            export companies is a win-win scenario that sustains local
            economies, ensures food security, and promotes responsible and
            eco-friendly agricultural practices.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </body>
</html>